title: Protesters in Cuba demand food and electricity as shortages bring hardship
description: Hundreds of people have taken to the streets in recent days in the city of Santiago.

title: 5 nonsensical ways to fill out your March Madness bracket
description: The deadline to fill out your March Madness bracket is coming up. If you want to participate but don't care or know anything about basketball, try these hairbrained rules for picking the winner.

title: A former nun explains why she ran away from her 'Cloistered' life
description: After her father died when she was 24, Catherine Coldstream entered a Carmelite monastery where she lived a life of prayer and obedience for 12 years. Her new memoir is Cloistered: My Years as a Nun.

title: In a boost for EVs, EPA finalizes strict new limits on tailpipe emissions
description: The Biden administration says it is imposing the "strongest-ever" tailpipe emission rules to protect public health and fight climate change.

title: Trump-endorsed Senate candidate Bernie Moreno wins Ohio's GOP Primary
description: The former car dealership owner beat out other primary challengers in a three-way race that tested former President Donald Trump's influence over Ohio GOP voters.
